<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184145>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Anterior end of Paleanotus bellis ((a) mCT-00097; (b–f) mCT-00104), imaged through micro- CT and rendered in 3D. (a) dorsal view; (b) dorsal view, virtually dissected to expose pharyngeal structures; (c) dorsal view, virtually dissected and rendered with lowered opacity to show position of jaws; (d) dorsal view, virtually dissected to expose pharyngeal structures; (e) lateral view, virtually dissected to expose pharyngeal structures. (f) Body cross section at level of jaws." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5184145/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184147>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Jaws of Paleanotus bellis (mCT-00104), imaged through micro-CT. (a) anterolateral view; (b) dorsal view and cross sections through the jaw along its length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5184147/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

